Package: summarystats
Title: Calculate Summary Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Eully", "Ao", , "eullyao@student.ubc.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-2887-1860"))
Description: The goal of summarystats is to calculate summary statistics (range, mean, median, and standard deviation) for a given variable within a dataset, grouped by another variable. Package dependency involves `dplyr` and `stats`.
